; Regression test for issue #1122: Explicit conversion from commodity with two fixed costs to primary commodity fails (BZ#1122)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1122
;
; Two postings with different explicit total costs {=amount} in the same
; transaction should balance correctly when the explicit EUR amount covers
; the sum of the fixed costs (1 EUR + 2 EUR = 3 EUR).

2015-05-16
  ACCOUNT1  1 COMMODITY {=1 EUR}
  ACCOUNT1  1 COMMODITY {=2 EUR}
  ACCOUNT2  -3 EUR

test bal -X EUR
               3 EUR  ACCOUNT1
              -3 EUR  ACCOUNT2
--------------------
                   0
end test
